I help companies solve complex backend challenges. Over the past decade, I've worked in teams at PayU and Urban Company on projects involving payment systems, high-scale architectures, and real-time platforms.

Some projects I've contributed to:

- Redesigning transaction infrastructure that scaled from 30 to 15,000 TPS per host
- Optimizing chat systems that reduced latency from 300ms to <75ms
- Building production management platforms for the fashion industry [\#Stream](stream.arjunverma.in)

I specialize in Ruby on Rails, Rust, Distributed Systems Architecture & System Design. Currently exploring machine learning and AI applications in backend systems.
